author: COMSOL
description:
In this benchmark a spherical cap subjected to a point load at the center. The resulting nonlinear deformation is studied using both Solid Mechanics and Shell interfaces. In both cases, a 2D axisymmetric formulation is used.

The results from both interfaces are compared with results given in the benchmark for different discretizations.
label: spherical_cap_with_central_point_load.mph
